title: Hyper Baby
description: Maria is a high school student, and is on her way to visit her sister in the hospital, who has just given birth to a baby boy. Things soon start to get strange when Maria sees an unusual (but extremely cute) boy at the hospital who is very interested in Maria's new nephew. The boy always seems to be hanging around, and only Maria seems to be able to see him! Is he a ghost? A demon? Why is Maria seeing him?
